MLS SUMMARIES for April 3
April 3 in Washington D.C.

DC United 2 San Jose 1. Goals: Moreno (Stewart) 12, Eskandarian (Moreno) 39; Ekelund pen. 19.

DC United -- Rimando, Namoff, Nelsen, Petke, Stewart, Carroll, Kovalenko, Olsen, Convey (Stokes, 89), Eskandarian (Adu, 61), Moreno (Gros, 85).

San Jose -- Onstad, Waibel, Agoos, Robinson, Corrales, Mullan, Ekelund (Ching, 74), Mulrooney, Russell (Alvarez, 86), De Rosario (Walker, 81), Donovan.

Yellow Cards: DC United -- Olsen 89; San Jose -- Robinson 21, De Rosario 23.

Red Cards: DC United -- Kovalenko 80; San Jose -- Waibel 76. Referee: Kevin Stott.

Att.: 24,603.

April 3 in Columbus

Columbus 1 MetroStars 3. Goals: Hejduk 30; Magee (Lisi) 40, Wolyniec (Lisi, Gaven) 52, Guevara 88.

Columbus -- Busch, Herdsman, Akwari (Oughton, 64), Fraser, Denton (Sutton, 85), Paule, Elliott, Martino, Hejduk, Testo (Ritch, 74), Cunningham.

MetroStars -- Walker, Leitch, Bonseu, Parke, Ziadie, Vaca, Guevara, Lisi (Clark, 66), Gaven, Magee (Taylor, 64), Wolyniec.

Yellow Cards: Columbus -- Hejduk 13, Martino 56, Cunningham 59, Elliott 83; MetroStars -- Craig Ziadie 57, Clark 86.

Referee: Abiodun Okulaja.

Att.: 20,356.

April 3 in Kansas City

Kansas City 0 Chicago 0.

Kansas City -- Meola, Zotinca, Conrad, Thomas, Garcia, Klein, Walsh (Gomez, 46), Zavagnin, Gutierrez, Arnaud, Wolff.

Chicago -- Ring, Whitfield, Curtin, Brown, Gray, Armas, Williams, Beasley, Ralph, Jaqua, Mapp (Razov, 66).

Yellow Cards: Kansas City -- Zotinca 20, Gutierrez 59; Chicago -- Armas 60.

Red Cards: Kansas City -- Klein 74; Chicago -- Brown 74.

Referee: Erich Simmons.

Att.: 20,229.

April 3 in Dallas

Dallas 1 Colorado 1. Goals: Rhine pen. 75; Spencer (Peguero, Chung) 36.

Dallas -- Garlick, Salyer, Gibbs, Jolley, Behncke (Pareja, 89), O'Brien, Davis, Valakari, Quill, Johnson, Nhleko (Rhine, 71).

Colorado -- Cannon, de la Torre, Borchers, Sullivan, Kotschau, Henderson, Beckerman, Powell, Chung, Peguero (Crawford, 89), Spencer.

Yellow Cards: Dallas -- Valakari 15, Gibbs 19; Colorado -- Powell 22, Henderson 66, Henderson 87.

Red Card: Colorado -- Henderson 87.

Referee: Terry Vaughn.

Att.: 7,359.

April 3 in Los Angeles

Los Angeles 3 New England 2. Goals: Ruiz (Torres) 30, Herzog (Ruiz) 59, Kirovski (Victorine) 69; Heaps (Cancela) 48, Noonan 68.

Los Angeles -- Hartman, Albright, Califf, Suarez, Marshall (Lewis, 46), Torres (Saragosa, 68), Herzog (Moreno, 88), Vagenas, Victorine, Kirovski, Ruiz.

New England -- Brown, Heaps, Kante (Dempsey, 83), Pierce, Franchino, Ralston, Cancela, Joseph, Noonan, Moore, Twellman.

Yellow Cards: New England -- Pierce 38, Kante 74.

Referee: Alex Prus.

Att.: 25,152.
